%C6%B0u-h%E1%BA%A7u/poem-xlAF2EsVCFr3TYqQlZWXRQ">Ngự đề Lưu hầu - 御題留侯</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-B%C3%ADch-San/author-GaA0SgEPvCmkAgLupJfzCQ">Trần Bích San</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Qu%C3%BD-C%C3%A1p/S%C4%A9-phu-t%E1%BB%B1-tr%E1%BB%8B-lu%E1%BA%ADn/poem-xa4a7rGY1wJjhCLHvtEZYg">Sĩ phu tự trị luận - 士夫自治論</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Qu%C3%BD-C%C3%A1p/author-BcCF1ZxvOmWV0_NgUZWaJw">Trần Quý Cáp</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/S%E1%BB%AD-T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-V%C3%A2n-%C4%91%C3%ADch-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-b3fujlv5fiGfU8on7S0RTA">Sử Tương Vân đích thi kỳ 1 - 史湘雲的詩其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/X%C3%A0-T%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/Th%E1%BA%A5t-t%E1%BB%8Bch-chu-trung/poem-PMdDGuheRxm6e6ZPv_Twnw">Thất tịch chu trung - 七夕舟中</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/X%C3%A0-T%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/author-OTOkL6TRbM0V41YwHIzvfA">Xà Tường</a>)<br></div>	</div>
